sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Researcher Agent
    participant A as Analyst Agent
    participant W as Writer Agent
    participant M as Memory

    R->>M: remember("Solar costs dropped 89% since 2010")
    R->>M: remember("Wind energy = 10% of US electricity")
    Note over M: Records saved under /crew/energy/agent/researcher

    A->>M: recall("energy statistics from researcher")
    M-->>A: Top matches from researcher scope

    A->>M: remember("Renewables now cost-competitive with fossil fuels")
    Note over M: Saved under /crew/energy/agent/analyst

    W->>M: recall("all findings and conclusions") via MemorySlice
    Note over M: MemorySlice searches BOTH researcher + analyst scopes
    M-->>W: Combined ranked results from both agents

    W->>W: Write final report using all findings
